data.description: What a view that is waiting for you! Wow! You can now come home to enjoy the restful, peaceful beauty of nature in all of its glory. Yes, it is waiting for you. The house is also one you will love too! Even though Sold-as-is.  Built in 1991 this Mountain Ridge home has been well taken care of. 3 BR/2.5ba, lovely foyer going into your living room and your dining room to the right. You also have a semi open kitchen to the den with a fireplace and entry into the sunroom and deck. Hardwood floors in the den and kitchen, carpet goes through most of the remainder of the house except for the foyer and laundry room. 1961 Sq Ft. Heated plus the Sunroom. part of the crawl space is a stand-up crawl space, so it is good for storage. With the exception of 2 bay windows and a small bathroom window, Window World replaced the windows in 2019, the buyer can continue the warranty with Window World for $50.00 within 30 days from closing! Take me home, country roads... Very close in proximity to Warm Springs, Calloway Gardens, Pine Mountain Valley, FD Roosevelt State Park at Pine Mountain, Wild Animal Safari. Like living in Vacation land!  New Deck on back of house!  Cash or Conventional, Sold in as-is condition.
